              <a href="/methodology/the-load-engine.html" style="color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">[ View Engine Specs → ]</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Readiness Engine</h3>
            <p>
              We built a check-in system that turns session feedback into practical load changes.
              <span class="accent">Simple enough to use consistently and useful enough to matter.</span>
            </p>
            <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);">
              <a href="/methodology/readiness-and-rpee.html" style="color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">[ View Engine Specs → ]</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Weak Point Engine</h3>
            <p>
              CMS carries weakness-specific alternates for common sticking points, so substitutions are not random.
              <span class="accent">Close-grip, board press, Spoto — tied to actual weak-link logic.</span>
            </p>
            <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);">
              <a href="/methodology/weak-point-analysis.html" style="color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">[ View Engine Specs → ]</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Joint Health & Longevity</h3>
            <p>
              The system monitors joint stress and automatically modifies training protocols to prevent overuse injury.
              <span class="accent">Train hard. Train forever.</span>
            </p>
            <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);">
              <a href="/methodology/joint-health-and-longevity.html" style="color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">[ View Engine Specs → ]</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Program Architectures</h3>
            <p>
              Three distinct engines: Bench Specialization for focused pressing strength, Jacked & Strong for balanced development, and SBD for full powerlifting competition.
              <span class="accent">Choose your path. CMS guides you to the goal.</span>
            </p>
            <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);">
              <a href="/methodology/program-architectures.html" style="color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">[ View Engine Specs → ]</a>
            </div>
          </article>
