            A <strong>macrocycle</strong> is the overall training structure that spans several weeks or months, typically leading up to a competition or training goal. Instead of guessing how to structure your training, a macrocycle works <strong>backward from your target date</strong>, ensuring every training phase builds toward peak performance on the platform.
          </p>
